                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-101-off553 t18280529-101-cd554"></join>, 2 sovereigns, 48 half-crowns, 30 shillings, and 20 sixpences, the monies of 
                     <persName id="t18280529-101-victim630" type="victimName">
                        Newman Francis Robinson 
                        McGowran
                     <interp inst="t18280529-101-victim630" type="surname" value="McGowran"></interp>
